Portions of the following files adapt and modify location-scale distributional
family code from the 'mgcv' package (file R/gamlss.r),
Copyright (C) Simon N. Wood, licensed GPL (>= 2):

  R/family-gausslss.R   adapted from mgcv::gaulss
  R/family-gammalss.R   adapted from mgcv::gammals

The modifications, by Ziwei Huang, are: a prior-weight-aware log-likelihood
(sum(wt * l0) and weighted per-observation derivative blocks), circlss family
metadata (param_names, param_circular, response_circular), and removal of the
discrete-design and neighbourhood-cross-validation code paths. Simon Wood neither
authored nor endorsed this package; his copyright is acknowledged here because his
code is adapted in the files above.

The combined work is distributed under GPL (>= 3) (GPL-3-or-later). 'mgcv' is
GPL (>= 2), which is compatible: GPL-2-or-later code may be used under GPL-3, so
it composes cleanly into this GPL-3-or-later package.
